Description:
Kingero, located in China sanitary ware base Chaozhou City, is a large enterprise that specialized in researching, designing, manufacturing and sales of ceramic sanitary ware. 
  

Foundation: 1993
Main Market:  North America, Southeast Asia, South America and Middle East Area;
Strong points: R&D Department, strong in innovation;
Technology: Super-Votex Flushing 3.5L single flush, 4.8L single flush, 3.0/4.5L dual flush;
